room_title: Escape room "Space Sector" by California State Escape in Sacramento
room_address: 5400 Power Inn Rd Ste B Sacramento, CA 95820
room_description:
You are a group of scientist working at Area 53, a top-secret government lab on the moon. The research you're doing has the potential to be extremely hazardous, and when you hear the sirens blaring "Quarantine initiated, please remain calm”, you know that remaining calm is the last thing you should do.
You have 60 minutes before the facility self-destructs. You must find a way to get yourself and Area 53’s valuable research back to earth before the self-destruct sequence is complete, but be careful, some of the research at Area 53 has been classified as HOSTILE.
